TopicTitle: Mechjeb is incompatible with KSP version 1.12.3.3173

Articles.Content:
I am not able to use Mechjeb because it is incompatible with my version of KSP (1.12.3.3173). All my friends can use Mechjeb and they are on the same version. I have no more mods installed.

Here is my log: https://www.dropbox.com/s/sncoyy5jw40hj40/Player.log?dl=0
Did you install it correctly? Make sure that your GameData folder contains only Squad, SquadExpansion and MechJeb folders as well as the ModuleManager DLL and config files.
You are running mechJeb2 v 2.5.1.0.  try updating to 2.7+
